'From Squeak2.9alpha of 17 July 2000 [latest update: #3164] on 12 December 2000 at 1:22:08 pm'!"Change Set:		playingProjectsDate:			12 December 2000Author:			Bob Arning- InternalThreadNavigationMorph, when dropped in a piano roll, will do a next project transition"!!InternalThreadNavigationMorph methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'RAA 12/12/2000 13:17'!triggerActionFromPianoRoll	| proj |	WorldState addDeferredUIMessage: [		self currentIndex >= listOfPages size ifTrue: [^1 beep].		currentIndex _ self currentIndex + 1.		proj _ Project named: ((listOfPages at: currentIndex) at: 1).		proj world setProperty: #letTheMusicPlay toValue: true.		proj enter.	]! !